---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import FeatureCard from "../components/FeatureCard.astro";

import panda1 from '../images/panda/panda1.png';
import panda2 from '../images/panda/panda2.png';
---

<Base pageTitle="Home">
  <Hero />

  <section id="content" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-justify">
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-16">
      wiRedPanda is a powerful and intuitive tool designed to help students, educators and enthusiasts on their journey of learning about digital circuits. With a user-friendly interface and advanced features, wiRedPanda transforms the process of understanding and creating circuits into an interactive and engaging experience.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-center mb-12">Main features</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16">
      <FeatureCard
        title="Real-Time Simulation"
        content="See your circuits come to life instantly as you make adjustments and experiment with different configurations."
      />
      <FeatureCard
        title="Intuitive Interface"
        content="Drag and drop elements, connect wires and build your circuits simply and efficiently."
      />
      <FeatureCard
        title="Detailed Analysis"
        content="Analyze your circuit with beWavedDolphin waveform simulator, identify and correct problems in your circuits."
      />
      <FeatureCard
        title="Cross-Platform"
        content="Available for Windows, macOS and Linux, ensuring that you can work on your project on any device."
      />
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center mb-16">
      <video autoplay muted loop class="w-full max-w-4xl rounded-xl border border-brand-blue/20 dark:border-brand-blue/40 shadow-lg shadow-black/20 dark:shadow-black/40">
        <source src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}demo.mp4`} type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 mb-16">
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed flex-1">
        We believe that technology education should be accessible, engaging and practical. Our software has been developed to simplify the learning process and allow you to focus on what really matters: understanding and creating digital circuits.
      </p>
      <Image
        src={panda1}
        alt="Screenshot of wiRedPanda application"
        width={500}
        class="rounded-xl border border-brand-blue/20 dark:border-brand-blue/40 shadow-lg shadow-black/20 dark:shadow-black/40 flex-shrink-0"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
      <Image
        src={panda2}
        alt="Screenshot of wiRedPanda application"
        width={500}
        class="rounded-xl border border-brand-blue/20 dark:border-brand-blue/40 shadow-lg shadow-black/20 dark:shadow-black/40 flex-shrink-0"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed flex-1">
        Download wiRedPanda now and start exploring the world of digital circuits. Try out all our features and see how we can help you achieve your goals. Already in use at Federal University of São Paulo, and maybe in your logic circuits class too!
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
